1.x.x, 2010-11-xx:
 + Notifier#default_options;
 + local cache;
 + severity (level) threshold;
 + compatibility with Ruby Logger. Exceptions:
   - Logger#info('initialize') { "Initializing..." } – ArgumentError
   - Logger#add(Logger::FATAL) { 'Fatal error!' }    – ArgumentError
   - and maybe something else

1.0.0, 2010-11-10:
 + initial stable version;
 * deprecated Gelf class is still there.
